    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Octopress: Building Your Own User Page for GitHub]]></title>
    <link href="http://lheberlie.github.io/blog/2014/07/31/hello-octopress/"/>
    <updated>2014-07-31T18:37:24-05:00</updated>
